# Anti-slop gate (Charles · Lucy · content)

When using **charles-linkedin-strategist** or **lucy-community-marketing**, or drafting LinkedIn/email/WhatsApp/marketing copy **or member-facing templates** (Brevo/admin email templates, invite/nurture/RSVP scripts):

